extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    28.12.2017.HK This class RequestDispatcherInfo represents the abstraction of a RequestDispatcher its stores informations about ApplicationVMInfo and can inspect cores resources, availability this reference can ask for Adding, Removing Core on the Processor of an ApplicationVM
